						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Fragment of a slab lying in the village chāvaḍi.</hi></p>						

						<p>12th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This record, in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">12th Century A.D.,</hi> registers a gift of income from toll on ten cattle for the benefit of the god Yōgēśvara, by Basavarasa with the permission of <hi rend="italic">Suṁkaveggaḍe</hi> <hi rend="bold">Vāmarasa</hi> at the instance of Bijjagāvuṇḍa.</p>						

						</summary>
